    "description": "If you're a passionate Backend Developer with drive and ambition, Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates in Coimbatore is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates:\nOracle India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Oracle India Asia Pacific Associates!",
